Text-Find-Scalar version 0.04
=============================

This module aims to support programmers in finding Scalars in any text. But
for parsing Perl programs, I highly recommend PPI from Adam Kennedy.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module has no dependencies

